de/\r\n    component2\r\n    -- src/\r\n    -- include/\r\n    ...etc...\r\n\r\nThis PR allows ignition projects to \\(optionally\\) balance this out a bit by accepting the following directory structure:\r\n\r\n    core\r\n    -- src/\r\n    -- include/\r\n    component1\r\n    -- src/\r\n    -- include/\r\n    component2\r\n    -- src/\r\n    -- include/\r\n    ...etc...\r\n\r\n`gnition-cmake` will check for a top-level `core` directory, and if it fails to find that, it will expect a top-level `src` and `include` directory like what we\u2019ve been using.\r\n\r\nThis is a backwards-compatible and mostly superficial change. It\u2019s currently being used in the new [ign-plugin](#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-plugin/src/NewRegistrationScheme/) repo, in case anyone wants to see some example usage.", "title": "Allow core library files to have their own directory", "destination": {"commit": {"hash": "c45056187ec1", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commit/c45056187ec1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commits/c45056187ec1"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}ts=default"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "ign-cmake", "full_name": "ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake", "uuid": "{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0-116b8e298901}"}, "branch": {"name": "default"}}, "reason": "", "source": {"commit": {"hash": "55b87cec6757", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commit/55b87cec6757.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/commits/55b87cec6757"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{3e77bcf7-f260-4cec-a1a0